 * name:Color Detection
 * function: you may see the color RGB value in the serial monitor
 * connection:
 * color sensor             uno r3
 * S0                       3
 * S1                       4
 * S2                       5
 * S3                       6
 * OUT                      2
 * GND                      GND
 * VCC                      5V
 ******************************************************/
